name: TWISTER I-6 LETTERS, still 2
description:
TWISTER I-6 LETTERS, still 2.
Still from TWISTER I-6 animation (OBJKT#229753), keyframe 29, 2500x2500 jpeg. 
Initially minted as single edition.

"Because most of the time I feel that all of my being is a love letter to you".

TWISTERS is a project about inconstant and changeable human nature and about different ways people may react to something that doesn't fit their expectations. 
TWISTERS is the original series of abstract animated artworks by Olga Feldman.
